summary: Gurthalak Voice of the Deeps - WoW Weapon - Remade and textured in blender by L33Nexus. Organized, placed and displayed in game by Pronam.
descriptionHtml:
~In dedication and memory of Eric West (Immok the Slayer)~
R.I.P. Immok The Slayer, 1992-2011
Sincerely,
The Scrollworks Community

-Gurthalak Voice of the Deeps- my first Skyrim mod Wooo!
Desc:
A two handed and single handed blade based on the World of Warcraft weapon.

Location:
Riverbank of Whiterun (Next to War Maidens)
-Check Images-

Possible Updates:
Daedric Style Re-textures

Issues:
Possible bug/clipping or handling placement.

Special thanks to:
Pronam for helping me get this in game and correcting a few bugs.

~New Mods Coming Soon~
author: L33Nexus - Pronam
